		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>One of your problems is easy to fix. The other is not. The first problem you had is a known bug with the stats and will be fixed in the next patch.<br />
<br />
The problem with your spell window is that there was a change to the spell icons when the UI went live. Replace EQUI_CastSpellWnd.xml and EQUI_Animations.xml with the files from your default. If replacing EQUI_Animations.xml messes up a mod then the person who made the mod is a dufus and will need to fix his mod before you will be able to use it.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
