	<td class="page">
	
		<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
		<tr valign="bottom">
			<td style="font-size:14pt">Wolfran</td>
			<td class="smallfont" align="right">07-31-2002 06:52 AM</td>
		</tr>
		</table>
		
		<hr />
		
		
			<div><strong>Found it!</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>Okay...Instead of using the UI_Animations.xml file included in Geddine's zip file, use the default one.  Just add the following lines to the &lt;texture info&gt; list:<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px;">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="alt2" style="border:1px">
			
				
                &lt;TextureInfo item = &quot;target.tga&quot;&gt;<br />
		&lt;Size&gt;<br />
			&lt;CX&gt;512&lt;/CX&gt;<br />
			&lt;CY&gt;64&lt;/CY&gt;<br />
		&lt;/Size&gt;<br />
	&lt;/TextureInfo&gt;<br />
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div><br />
<br />
You also want to add the following:<br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px;">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="alt2" style="border:1px">
			
				
&lt;!-- Target Gauge Parts --&gt;<br />
<br />
	&lt;Ui2DAnimation item = &quot;A_TargetGaugeBackground&quot;&gt;<br />
		&lt;Cycle&gt;true&lt;/Cycle&gt;<br />
		&lt;Frames&gt;<br />
			&lt;Texture&gt;target.tga&lt;/Texture&gt;<br />
			&lt;Location&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;0&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Location&gt;<br />
			&lt;Size&gt;<br />
				&lt;CX&gt;400&lt;/CX&gt;<br />
				&lt;CY&gt;8&lt;/CY&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Size&gt;<br />
			&lt;Hotspot&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;0&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Hotspot&gt;<br />
			&lt;Duration&gt;1000&lt;/Duration&gt;<br />
		&lt;/Frames&gt;<br />
	&lt;/Ui2DAnimation&gt;<br />
	&lt;Ui2DAnimation item = &quot;A_TargetGaugeFill&quot;&gt;<br />
		&lt;Cycle&gt;true&lt;/Cycle&gt;<br />
		&lt;Frames&gt;<br />
			&lt;Texture&gt;target.tga&lt;/Texture&gt;<br />
			&lt;Location&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;10&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Location&gt;<br />
			&lt;Size&gt;<br />
				&lt;CX&gt;400&lt;/CX&gt;<br />
				&lt;CY&gt;8&lt;/CY&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Size&gt;<br />
			&lt;Hotspot&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;0&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Hotspot&gt;<br />
			&lt;Duration&gt;1000&lt;/Duration&gt;<br />
		&lt;/Frames&gt;<br />
	&lt;/Ui2DAnimation&gt;<br />
	&lt;Ui2DAnimation item = &quot;A_TargetGaugeLines&quot;&gt;<br />
		&lt;Cycle&gt;true&lt;/Cycle&gt;<br />
		&lt;Frames&gt;<br />
			&lt;Texture&gt;target.tga&lt;/Texture&gt;<br />
			&lt;Location&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;20&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Location&gt;<br />
			&lt;Size&gt;<br />
				&lt;CX&gt;400&lt;/CX&gt;<br />
				&lt;CY&gt;8&lt;/CY&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Size&gt;<br />
			&lt;Hotspot&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;0&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Hotspot&gt;<br />
			&lt;Duration&gt;1000&lt;/Duration&gt;<br />
		&lt;/Frames&gt;<br />
	&lt;/Ui2DAnimation&gt;<br />
	&lt;Ui2DAnimation item = &quot;A_TargetGaugeLinesFill&quot;&gt;<br />
		&lt;Cycle&gt;true&lt;/Cycle&gt;<br />
		&lt;Frames&gt;<br />
			&lt;Texture&gt;target.tga&lt;/Texture&gt;<br />
			&lt;Location&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;30&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Location&gt;<br />
			&lt;Size&gt;<br />
				&lt;CX&gt;400&lt;/CX&gt;<br />
				&lt;CY&gt;8&lt;/CY&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Size&gt;<br />
			&lt;Hotspot&gt;<br />
				&lt;X&gt;0&lt;/X&gt;<br />
				&lt;Y&gt;0&lt;/Y&gt;<br />
			&lt;/Hotspot&gt;<br />
			&lt;Duration&gt;1000&lt;/Duration&gt;<br />
		&lt;/Frames&gt;<br />
	&lt;/Ui2DAnimation&gt;<br />
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div><br />
<br />
<br />
From what I understand, these can be added anywhere in to file.  As I said...still learning.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
